729289f-a.title: Richmond: Prospect Street - Bay Street
729289f-a.text:
Prospect Street, north side, east from Bay Street
to the Staten Island Railroad tracks. The last 2-story house
is that of Swift \&. Co.
April 19,1929
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

729288f-a.text:
(1)
Prospect Street, south side, between Bay and Front

May 25, 1935
P. L. Sperr
